title: Win a FREE 'Equestria Girls Friendship Games' Prize Pack!
text: Win a FREE 'Equestria Girls Friendship Games' Prize Pack! Thursday, 22 October 2015 (10 minutes ago) Who just loved Twilight Sparkle‘s photo diary she did for JustJaredJr.com last week?!
